    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_24667-24736",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "24667-24736",
      "markText": "加加林抬头望去，这时，地核文明十万年的探索得到了最后的抱偿。 他看到了灿烂的星空。",
      "totalCount": 6030,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=24667&rangeEnd=24736",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=24667&rangeEnd=24736"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_1502-1539",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "1502-1539",
      "markText": "山的魅力是从两个方位感受到的：一是从平原上远远地看山，再就是站在山顶上。”",
      "totalCount": 4560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1502&rangeEnd=1539",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1502&rangeEnd=1539"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_7182-7259",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "7182-7259",
      "markText": "冯帆说，“船长，还有一件事我没告诉你，在珠峰遇难的那4名大学登山队员中，有我的恋人。当我割断登山索时，脑子里闪过的念头是这样的：我不能死，还有别的山呢。”",
      "totalCount": 3684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=7182&rangeEnd=7259",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=7182&rangeEnd=7259"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_27922-27937",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "27922-27937",
      "markText": "他必须活下去，因为山无处不在。",
      "totalCount": 3360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=27922&rangeEnd=27937",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=27922&rangeEnd=27937"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_25807-25828",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "25807-25828",
      "markText": "那我告诉你，这是一个200亿半径的泡世界。",
      "totalCount": 3213,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=25807&rangeEnd=25828",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=25807&rangeEnd=25828"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_12484-12497",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "12484-12497",
      "markText": "山无处不在，只是登法不同。",
      "totalCount": 3120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=12484&rangeEnd=12497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=12484&rangeEnd=12497"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_20643-20663",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "20643-20663",
      "markText": "没什么可激动的，“螺旋”号到达的是海底。",
      "totalCount": 2535,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=20643&rangeEnd=20663",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=20643&rangeEnd=20663"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_1364-1407",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "1364-1407",
      "markText": "“这你错了，”冯帆说，“山里长大的人一般都不喜欢山，在他们感觉中山把自己与世界隔绝了。",
      "totalCount": 2482,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1364&rangeEnd=1407",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1364&rangeEnd=1407"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_7769-7783",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "7769-7783",
      "markText": "他成为第一个游着泳登山的人。",
      "totalCount": 2394,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=7769&rangeEnd=7783",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=7769&rangeEnd=7783"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_618-643",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "618-643",
      "markText": "“我是不是让你想到了那部叫《海上钢琴师》的电影？”",
      "totalCount": 2175,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=618&rangeEnd=643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=618&rangeEnd=643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_27864-27893",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "27864-27893",
      "markText": "如果现在真有什么可背叛的东西来拯救自己的生命，他会背叛的。",
      "totalCount": 2156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=27864&rangeEnd=27893",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=27864&rangeEnd=27893"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_15271-15328",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "15271-15328",
      "markText": "船上其余的人，包括船长，都被哥白尼当食物吃掉了，事实上，这种把船员当给养的方式，是地层探险早期效率最高的航行方式。",
      "totalCount": 2085,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=15271&rangeEnd=15328",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=15271&rangeEnd=15328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_14200-14230",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "14200-14230",
      "markText": "不，没什么教会，一个看不到太阳和星空的文明是产生不了宗教的。",
      "totalCount": 2040,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=14200&rangeEnd=14230",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=14200&rangeEnd=14230"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_27431-27519",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "27431-27519",
      "markText": "冯帆仰望着星空，想像着那个遥远的世界，真的太远了，连光都会走得疲惫，那又是很早以前，在那个海面上，泡世界的加加林也像他现在这样仰望着星空。穿越广漠的时空荒漠，他们的灵魂相通了。",
      "totalCount": 1904,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=27431&rangeEnd=27519",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=27431&rangeEnd=27519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_24579-24638",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "24579-24638",
      "markText": "我感到这是一支无形的巨手温柔的抚摸，这巨手来自一个我们不知道的无限巨大的存在，在这个存在面前，我变成了另一个全新的我。",
      "totalCount": 1620,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=24579&rangeEnd=24638",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=24579&rangeEnd=24638"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_14795-14839",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "14795-14839",
      "markText": "在一个刚能容身的小小空洞里机器般劳作，在幽闭中追寻着渺茫的希望，无疑需要巨大的精神力量。",
      "totalCount": 1616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=14795&rangeEnd=14839",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ac132cd071a2727bac1b359?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=14795&rangeEnd=14839"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27423355_40_12600-12632",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "12600-12632",
      "markText": "对于我们来说，周围都是山，这山把我们封闭了，我们要挖洞才能登山。",
      "totalCount": 1598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27423355&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=12600&rangeEnd=12632",
